Yeremia o lning'o lo sotua


1  Nelotu ororei enetii Yeremia eing'uaa Olaitoriani ejo: 
2  “Toning'o irorei lele ning'o lo sotua, nirorie iltung'ana le Yuda o lelo oomanya Yerusalem. 
3  Tiaaki iyie ninche, nji ejo Olaitoriani, Enkai e Israel: ediaa ilo tung'ani lemening irorei lele ning'o lo sotua. 
4  Ilo laitanapa apa iloo papaai linyi pee ayau nanu ninche aitupuku te nkop e Misiri, aitung'uaa ilo kokuet le sekenkei, ajo, “Entoning oltoilo lai, niasiasa nena pooki naitanap nanu intae. Pee iyakuku intae iltung'ana laainei, naaku nanu Enkai inyi, 
5  pee atum ataasa olmumai lai apa lainosa nanu too loo papaai linyi, pee aisho nanu ninche enkop naruko kule o naishi, anaa enatiu ena olong.” Nawal nanu ajo, “Metotiwuo neijia Olaitoriani.”


6  Naajoki nanu Olaitoriani, “Ntudupai kulo rorei pooki tiatua nkanas e Yuda, o too nkoitoi naalala e Yerusalem. Entoning irorei lele ning'o lo sotua niasiasa. 
7  Amu aikoo nanu loo papaai linyi akurraki ina kata apa pee ayau nanu ninche ailepunye aitung'uaa enkop e Misiri, naikok aitirrishaki, o tena olong, ajo, entoning oltoilo lai. 
8  Ore eyia eitu ninche ening kake eshomo ake pooki ng'ae te ngolon oltau lenye torrono. Neaku ayawua nanu shumata ninche irorei pooki lele ning'o lo sotua apa laitanapa nanu ninche metaasa, kake eitu ninche eas.”


9  Naaigil nanu Olaitoriani ajoki, “Etii enkiseroto atua iltung'ana le Yuda o lelo oomanya Yerusalem. 
10  Eibelekenyate ninche aashukokino ntorrok oo loo nkakuyiaa lenye, apa ootanyaita ening irorei laainei; eshomo ninche aasujaa kulie aitin pee eisiaai ninche; etudung'o enkaji e Israel o enkaji e Yuda osotua lai apa laitobira nanu tenebo loo papaai lenye. 
11  Neaku, nji ejo Olaitoriani, ng'ura kayau nanu entorroni shumata ninche nemeidim aatapaashare; ore hoo naaishiraki ninche nanu, maning nanu ninche. 
12  Nepuo nkanas e Yuda o lelo oomanya Yerusalem aaishiraki nena aitin naapejoki ninche enkorropil, kake meidim ninche aaitajeu ninche te nkata e nyamali enye. 
13  Amu etaa kumok nkaitin inyi anaa nkanas inyi, iyie Yuda; naa kumok anaa nkoitoi naalala e Yerusalem lperereni loo lasarri nintobira pee intukurrurru ate te lelo perereni loo lasarri oopejokinyeki Baal enkorropil.


14  “Metaa miomonoki iyie kulo tung'ana, arashu ilepie enkishirata arashu enkomono te rishata enye, amu mainining nanu tenaaipot ninche nanu tenkata enye enyamali. 
15  Kaa sipata eeta ina nanyor nanu tiatua enkop ai, eidipa ataasa nkiaasin torrok? Keidim ilmuma o nkiri naaitaikiaki olasar aaiwuang'ie enkidaata ino? Eikintiship naa iyie ina? 
16  Kimpoto apa iyie Olaitoriani ajo, “Oloirien onyori, obore ilng'anayio sidain;’ kake te nkikurrukur e ndarata sapuk epik ninye atua enkima, ore ilng'osil lenyena nemut enkima. 
17  Ore Olaitoriani loo lororani, laa ninye apa likituuno iyie, kitudung'oko iyie entorrono, te nkaraki ina torrono nataasa enkaji e Israel o enkaji e Yuda, naaitagor nanu aapejoki Baal enkorropil.”

Etarreshoki Yeremia pee eari metua


18  Naaitayiolo nanu Olaitoriani nayiolou nanu; nikintoki iyie aitodol nanu nkiaasin enye torrok.


19  Kake atiu apa nanu anaa olkuoo le ker obor oriki aapuo aayieng. Eitu apa nanu ayiolou ajo nanu eitobiraki ninche entorroni ejo, “Mainyala iyiook olchani tenebo ilng'anayio lenyena, matudung iyiook aaiwuang'ie te nkop oo looishu, pee meitokini ae kata aadamu enkarna enye.”


20  Kake ore, iyie Olaitoriani loo lororani, oiguana te sipata, ilo otem oltau o ndamunot nchooki nanu matoduaa elap ino te shumata ninche, amu iyie nanu aigarakine too mbaa aainei.


21  Neaku nji ejo Olaitoriani tialo lelo tung'ana le Anatot, lelo ooing'oru enkishui ino nejo, “Mimbonisho te nkarna Olaitoriani, arashu iye te nkaina ang” 
22  neaku nji ejo Olaitoriani loo lororani: “Ng'ura, kaitame nanu ninche; keye lelo barnot to lalem; ore layiok lenye o ntoyie enye neye to lameyu; 
23  nemeetae obo lenye oleku. Amu kayau nanu entorroni shumata iltung'ana le Anatot, teilo ari le nkitamioto enye.”

